end,    ::ffff:127.0.0.1, GET, /check-state,                  403, http://localhost:4200/, Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_12_6) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/62.0.3202.94 Safari/537.36,  --47ms--
